TASK:
Design the single most impactful infographic from these insights. Choose the visual format that best fits the data:
- 2×2 matrix (positioning/comparison)
- Flow diagram (process/sequence)
- Comparison table (before/after, tool A vs B)
- Taxonomy / hierarchy (classification of concepts)
- Timeline (evolution of a trend)
- Stat-focused layout (big numbers + context)

Return the following sections exactly:

## INFOGRAPHIC CONCEPT
[Visual type and what it shows in 2 sentences]

## CONTENT STRUCTURE
[Describe the layout in detail: sections, labels, data to display, what goes where]

## IMAGE GENERATION PROMPT
Generate a comprehensive DALL-E / ChatGPT image prompt (150–200 words) that specifies:
- Visual style: professional, dark-themed data visualization, LinkedIn-appropriate
- Exact layout and structure
- Color palette: #0D1117 background, #0077B5 LinkedIn blue accents, #FFFFFF primary text, #8B949E secondary text
- Specific text labels, numbers, and section names to include
- Square format (1080×1080px)
- No photorealistic elements — clean vector/graphic style
- Do NOT ask for faces, logos, or copyrighted branding

## LINKEDIN CAPTION
[150–200 word caption to accompany the infographic.
Structure: bold hook → what the visual shows → 2–3 key takeaways → question for engagement.
Tone: practitioner-level, direct, no hype.]

